data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION!!! This exquisite 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo located in the heart of Valley Ranch! This Coppell ISD residence offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it an ideal home for those seeking a vibrant and modern lifestyle. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting living space adorned with tasteful finishes and an abundance of natural light. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating a perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat, offering a peaceful sanctuary after a long day. It boasts generous space, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom complete with a luxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, and dual vanities. The second bedroom is equally spacious and offers versatility to be used as a guest room, home office, or a personalized space to suit your needs. Community pool, spa and jogging paths at your connivence!
